item.title: CVE-2022-22410|2024-09-17T03:08:26.329Z -- ibm -- watson%20query
item.description: IBM Watson Query with Cloud Pak for Data as a Service could allow an authenticated user to obtain sensitive information that would allow them to examine or alter system configurations or data sources connected to the service. IBM X-Force ID: 222763.
